name: testEditEmailOnTheUserProfilePageByDropDown
description: The 'Email' can be edited to the created User from Profile page by drop-down menu
descriptionHtml: The 'Email' can be edited to the created User from Profile page by drop-down menu

testStage.description: The 'Email' can be edited to the created User from Profile page by drop-down menu

steps.name: click 'Manage Jenkins' link from Main page
Click Manage Users on ManageJenkins Page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
click 'Manage Jenkins' link from Main page
Click Manage Users on ManageJenkins Page
Select 'Configure' menu item in User ID Dropdown menu
Delete the current E-mail address and type a new one
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
